======================================================================
  策略 2（各自变换）: hd09.txt
======================================================================

  原始输入 (32): i9, i8, i7, i6, i5, i4, i31, i30, i3, i29, i28, i27, i26, i25, i24, i23, i22, i21, i20, i2, i19, i18, i17, i16, i15, i14, i13, i12, i11, i10, i1, i0
  输出函数: 32 个 (16 非平凡)

  各输出在 g-space 中的紧凑形式：

  om_0:
    z_0 = NOR(i0, i1, ..., i15)
    g(z) = 1 xor z_0 xor i_16 * z_0
    T=2

  om_1:
    = i_17 * NOR(i0..i15) * NOT(i16) * ... * NOT(i_16)
    -> g-space: T=1

  om_2:
    = i_18 * NOR(i0..i15) * NOT(i16) * ... * NOT(i_17)
    -> g-space: T=1

  om_3:
    = i_19 * NOR(i0..i15) * NOT(i16) * ... * NOT(i_18)
    -> g-space: T=1

  om_4:
    = i_20 * NOR(i0..i15) * NOT(i16) * ... * NOT(i_19)
    -> g-space: T=1

  om_5:
    = i_21 * NOR(i0..i15) * NOT(i16) * ... * NOT(i_20)
    -> g-space: T=1

  om_6:
    = i_22 * NOR(i0..i15) * NOT(i16) * ... * NOT(i_21)
    -> g-space: T=1

  om_7:
    = i_23 * NOR(i0..i15) * NOT(i16) * ... * NOT(i_22)
    -> g-space: T=1

  om_8:
    = i_24 * NOR(i0..i15) * NOT(i16) * ... * NOT(i_23)
    -> g-space: T=1

  om_9:
    = i_25 * NOR(i0..i15) * NOT(i16) * ... * NOT(i_24)
    -> g-space: T=1

  om_10:
    = i_26 * NOR(i0..i15) * NOT(i16) * ... * NOT(i_25)
    -> g-space: T=1

  om_11:
    = i_27 * NOR(i0..i15) * NOT(i16) * ... * NOT(i_26)
    -> g-space: T=1

  om_12:
    = i_28 * NOR(i0..i15) * NOT(i16) * ... * NOT(i_27)
    -> g-space: T=1

  om_13:
    = i_29 * NOR(i0..i15) * NOT(i16) * ... * NOT(i_28)
    -> g-space: T=1

  om_14:
    = i_30 * NOR(i0..i15) * NOT(i16) * ... * NOT(i_29)
    -> g-space: T=1

  om_15:
    = i_31 * NOR(i0..i15) * NOT(i16) * ... * NOT(i_30)
    -> g-space: T=1

  总 T(g) = 17

  TNode 解析器因跨空间 XOR 无法自动提取。
  但函数本身具有高度可简化性（T=17, 每输出 T=1-2）。

